        "gg534V2lnCv_text": "<p>90-Day Hassle-Free Returns &amp; 2-Year Warranty</p>",
        "ggyRBy0ohEh_childItem_0": "<p><span style=\"font-size:13px;\">ELŌA is trusted by over </span><span style=\"color:#EE9A94;font-size:13px;\"><strong>125k+ Americans</strong></span></p>",
        "ggyKCLJ8a_V_text": "<span style=\"font-size:24px;\">Your body isn’t the problem. Your clothes are.</span>",
        "ggOGvw2uK6P_text": "<p>The reason you still see belly fat, love handles and skin texture in every top…</p><p>…is because regular shirts <strong>don’t shape anything. </strong>They just <i>show everything.</i><br><br><strong>ÉLOA fixes that instantly.</strong></p><p><strong>3D Sculpting Technology™</strong> smooths the look and shapes your waist <strong>the second you put it on.</strong></p><p>✔ Snatched waist effect<br>✔ Smoother belly look<br>✔ Lifted bust look<br>✔ Better silhouette under clothes</p><p><strong>You don’t need a new body. You need the right tee.</strong></p>"
      }
