    "gp_section_603346966390244055": {
      "type": "gp-section-603346966390244055",
      "settings": {
        "checksum": "342b450bcd5f10a356916d7667e32e79bc336907d3d759faeaf993e415d35959_1_1_0_0__1",
        "ggV66t7CVol_childItem_0": "<p><span style=\"color:#000000;\">Materials &amp; Care</span></p>",
        "ggV66t7CVol_childItem_1": "<p><strong>&nbsp;FREE RETURNS &amp; Exchanges</strong></p>",
        "gg-dZbzIeuj_text": "<p><strong>Composition:</strong> 57% Polyamide, 43% Elastane</p><p>&nbsp;</p><p><strong>Care Instructions:</strong></p><p>&nbsp;</p><ul><li>Wash at temperatures below 40°C</li><li>Do not bleach</li><li>Do not iron</li><li>Do not dry clean</li></ul>",
        "ggHaLbhbPo4_text": "<p><span style=\"font-size:13px;\">We believe in hassle-free shopping.</span><br><br><span style=\"font-size:13px;\"><strong>Estimated Delivery Times:</strong></span></p><ul><li><span style=\"font-size:13px;\"><strong>UK &amp; EU:</strong>&nbsp;8-12 business days&nbsp;</span></li><li><span style=\"font-size:13px;\"><strong>US &amp; Canada:</strong>&nbsp;4 to 12 business days</span></li><li><span style=\"font-size:13px;\"><strong>Rest of the World:</strong>&nbsp;8-15 business days&nbsp;</span><br><br><span style=\"font-size:13px;\"><strong>- 90-Day Return Window</strong>: If you’re still unsatisfied, you may return your item within 45 days of delivery for a refund.</span><br><br><span style=\"font-size:13px;\"><strong>- Money-Back Guarantee</strong>: Once we receive the returned item in its original condition, we’ll process your refund.</span></li></ul>",
        "ggmzLhi-ljn_childItem_0": "<p>reviews</p>",
        "ggdNAueEkoC_text": "<p>The 3D shaping is actually visible.</p>",
        "gg1-ZKocESm_text": "<p>I thought it was just marketing, but you can literally see the difference when you put it on. My waist looks tighter and my belly looks smoother immediately.</p>",
        "ggggrwoLGS__text": "<p>Margot H.</p>",
        "ggORXewsPBB_text": "<p>Verified Buyer</p>",
        "ggzMRLKssKK_text": "<p>The Perfect Gift</p>",
        "ggyWML2cdgn_text": "<p>Got this for my husband’s birthday and he hasn’t taken it off since. It matches everything he wears and the spinning rotor is such a cool detail. He says it’s one of the best gifts I’ve ever given him. Super classy and well made!</p>",
        "ggX50r-F1f3_text": "<p>Olivia J.</p>",
        "gga9ifit7kz_text": "<p>Verified Buyer</p>",
        "ggiqGqP7jVp_text": "<p>I didn’t expect to feel this confident so fast.</p>",
        "ggvOm1GF6hu_text": "<p>I didn’t change my diet or routine, but seeing a smoother waist in the mirror instantly made me feel better. It’s the first time in a long time I actually liked how I looked in a fitted top.</p>",
        "ggDWQKfSkTu_text": "<p>Karine N.</p>",
        "gg21WCNBJX4_text": "<p>Verified Buyer</p>",
        "gg0kqiBWosj_text": "<p>My belly is the first thing I notice… and this fixed it.</p>",
        "gg56Y3gCxIT_text": "<p>I always felt insecure about my lower belly showing through shirts. The first time I wore Elōa, everything looked smoother and more “snatched” instantly.</p>",
        "ggEXlXo6pOb_text": "<p>Meggy J.</p>",
        "ggt81-6qRlx_text": "<p>Verified Buyer</p>",
        "ggRcFobOsyx_text": "<p>This is what I wanted shapewear to be.</p>",
        "ggfXjbVnKDf_text": "<p>Most shapewear made me look weird or created bulges. Elōa just makes my silhouette look clean and natural, like my body but upgraded.</p>",
        "gg_RjLn1yIv_text": "<p>Marta C.</p>",
        "ggui3ncSB5m_text": "<p>Verified Buyer</p>",
        "ggi2_S5dYAi_text": "<p>I look better in EVERY outfit now.</p>",
        "ggHI6suLSFf_text": "<p>Even my basic jeans + tee outfits look more flattering. My waist looks more defined and my top sits so much nicer on my body.</p>",
        "ggZYfcGr3Ek_text": "<p>Jade K.</p>",
        "ggVQb5cCw_c_text": "<p>Verified Buyer</p>",
        "gglbb0LRzeD_text": "<p>Rated <span style=\"color:#00B67A;\"><strong>4.7</strong></span>/ 5 based on <span style=\"color:#00B67A;\"><strong><u>1897 Reviews.</u></strong></span></p>"
      }
    },
