    "gp_section_603346966457352919": {
      "type": "gp-section-603346966457352919",
      "settings": {
        "checksum": "f9151ebd304f383691ac3ac5e4b2d7b433dec960cabc0e20bd7c7dd868154ad4_1_1_0_0__1",
        "ggvyreBNINt_text": "<p><span style=\"font-size:12px;\">Still have questions ? Check here</span></p>",
        "ggX2EniVm9q_text": "<span style=\"font-size:30px;\">FREQUENTLY <i>ASKED</i> &nbsp;QUESTIONS</span>",
        "ggR2-nH2eM0_childItem_0": "<p><span style=\"background-color:rgb(255,255,255);color:rgb(28,28,28);font-size:16px;\">How does Eloa’s 3D Sculpting Technology™ work?</span></p>",
        "ggR2-nH2eM0_childItem_1": "<p><span style=\"background-color:rgb(255,255,255);color:rgb(28,28,28);font-size:16px;\">Is the result instant or does it take time?</span></p>",
        "ggR2-nH2eM0_childItem_2": "<p><span style=\"background-color:rgb(255,255,255);color:rgb(28,28,28);font-size:16px;\">Does it roll up?</span></p>",
        "ggR2-nH2eM0_childItem_3": "<p><span style=\"background-color:rgb(255,255,255);color:rgb(28,28,28);font-size:16px;\">How do I wash and care for it?</span></p>",
        "ggR2-nH2eM0_childItem_4": "<p><span style=\"font-size:16px;\">How long does shipping take?</span></p>",
        "ggR2-nH2eM0_childItem_5": "<p><span style=\"font-size:16px;\">What is your return policy?</span></p>",
        "ggXHYiMjwOM_text": "<p>Eloa’s <strong>3D Compression Zones™</strong> create resistance around your core, forcing your muscles to work harder with every movement.&nbsp;</p><p>&nbsp;</p><p>When your muscles work harder, they burn more energy to produce it — even during simple daily activities.<br>That’s why women often feel more “engaged”, stay consistent longer, and start seeing results faster.</p>",
        "ggoQB6YO3wQ_text": "<p>From the very first wear, Eloa gives you a <strong>smoother silhouette</strong> and a more <strong>snatched waist look</strong>.<br>Most customers notice:</p><p>&nbsp;</p><p><span style=\"background-color:rgba(247,247,247,0);color:rgba(0,0,0,0.85);font-size:15px;\">✔ </span><span style=\"font-size:15px;\">belly looks flatter instantly</span></p><p><span style=\"background-color:rgba(247,247,247,0);color:rgba(0,0,0,0.85);font-size:15px;\">✔ </span><span style=\"font-size:15px;\">waist looks more defined</span></p><p><span style=\"background-color:rgba(247,247,247,0);color:rgba(0,0,0,0.85);font-size:15px;\">✔ </span><span style=\"font-size:15px;\">bust looks lifted and supported</span></p><p><span style=\"background-color:rgba(247,247,247,0);color:rgba(0,0,0,0.85);font-size:15px;\">✔ a cleaner silhouette under clothes</span></p><p>&nbsp;</p>",
        "gggxLjRu8yN_text": "<p>Eloa is designed to stay in place thanks to its structured 3D zones.<br>If rolling happens, it’s usually a sizing issue — check the size guide (and size up if you’re between sizes).</p>",
        "ggkDSqjyiH9_text": "<p><span style=\"background-color:rgba(247, 247, 247, 0);color:rgba(0,0,0,0.85);font-size:13.6px;\">To keep your garment looking new:</span><br><br><span style=\"background-color:rgba(247, 247, 247, 0);color:rgba(0,0,0,0.85);font-size:13.6px;\">✔ Machine wash cold</span><br><br><span style=\"background-color:rgba(247, 247, 247, 0);color:rgba(0,0,0,0.85);font-size:13.6px;\">✔ Wash with like colors</span><br><br><span style=\"background-color:rgba(247, 247, 247, 0);color:rgba(0,0,0,0.85);font-size:13.6px;\">✔ Tumble dry low or hang dry for best results</span></p>",
        "ggo6IN6uaum_text": "<p>🚚 <strong>Fast &amp; Secure Shipping — Worldwide 🌍</strong></p><p>&nbsp;</p><p>🇺🇸 <strong>US Orders</strong><br>If your item is in stock at our US warehouse, expect delivery in <strong>3–5 business days</strong>.<br>Otherwise, allow <strong>7–12 business days</strong>, depending on availability.</p><p>&nbsp;</p><p>🇬🇧 <strong>UK Orders</strong><br>Most UK deliveries arrive within <strong>7–12 business days</strong>, depending on availability.</p><p>&nbsp;</p><p>🌐 <strong>International Orders</strong><br>Most international deliveries arrive within <strong>7–14 business days</strong>, depending on your location.</p><p>&nbsp;</p><p>📦 <strong>Order Tracking</strong><br>As soon as your order ships, you’ll receive a <strong>tracking number by email</strong> to monitor your delivery in real time.</p><p>&nbsp;</p><p>🛡️ <strong>Shipping Guarantee</strong><br>If your item arrives damaged, don’t worry — you’re protected by our <strong>Shipping Guarantee</strong>.<br>Just contact us, and we’ll send you a <strong>free replacement</strong>. No hassle. No extra cost.</p>",
        "ggNjTt3JeWU_text": "<p>We offer a <strong>90-Day Money-Back Guarantee</strong>! If you’re not completely satisfied, return it for a <strong>full refund – no questions asked.</strong></p>",
        "ggJogWG4aSB_label": "<p><span style=\"font-size:13px;\"><strong>TRY IT RISK-FREE - TODAY AT 60% OFF!</strong></span></p>",
        "ggykT7DQPkE_text": "<p><span style=\"color:#232E3E;\"><strong>45-day</strong></span> money&nbsp;<br>back guarantee</p>",
        "ggwKdXOJiMm_text": "<p><span style=\"color:#232E3E;\"><strong>free returns</strong></span><strong>,</strong> NO QUESTIONS ASKED&nbsp;</p>"
      }
    },
    "gp_section_603346966457418455": {
      "type": "gp-section-603346966457418455",
      "settings": {
        "checksum": "34185e8d49a3c84bdb57b70a0d2d2a8f96301d388c2b99641bc1c4c529b9e7c2_1_1_0_0__1",
        "ggX3BDxKCDi_text": "<p><span style=\"color:#FFFFFF;font-size:14px;\">“Out of all the sculpting tees we tested, none came close to the Eloa 3D Compression Tee.</span><br><span style=\"color:#FFFFFF;font-size:14px;\">It’s the fastest ‘before &amp; after’ we’ve seen from a tee.”</span></p>",
        "ggYSoxxmRYH_text": "<p><span style=\"color:#FFFFFF;font-size:14px;\">“From basic outfit to sculpted silhouette — in seconds.</span><br><span style=\"color:#FFFFFF;font-size:14px;\">This is the kind of shaping you notice immediately.”</span></p>",
        "ggMiRCe5hBz_text": "<p><span style=\"color:#FFFFFF;\">“3D sculpting zones that actually show results.</span><br><span style=\"color:#FFFFFF;\">Smoother belly, defined waist, and a cleaner silhouette under clothes.”</span></p>"
      }
    },
