    "gp_section_603346966474195671": {
      "type": "gp-section-603346966474195671",
      "settings": {
        "checksum": "b6c86fe9413b24425b77ea00f1eabaadbd51da51fb040b1088905b00c453636a_1_1_0_0__1",
        "ggSFH2F6tDC_text": "<p><span style=\"color:#000000;font-size:20px;\"><strong>High-Performance Compression Fabric</strong></span></p>",
        "ggguyBwSsXe_text": "<p>Engineered to last, designed to move with your body.<br>Ultra-soft, breathable, and supportive — without irritation or stiffness.</p>",
        "ggPNkqXZdnw_text": "<p><span style=\"color:#070707;font-size:20px;\"><strong>Powered by 3D Compression Technology™</strong></span></p>",
        "gge5s6wWdct_text": "<p>Zoned, intelligent compression that supports posture, muscle engagement, and body awareness — delivering consistent sculpting and support throughout the day.</p>",
        "ggF9aQjr8k5_text": "<p><span style=\"color:#070707;font-size:20px;\"><strong>Breathable &amp; Sweat-Resistant</strong></span></p>",
        "ggJTa6o1O8K_text": "<p>Keeps you cool and comfortable during daily wear, work, or light activity.<br>No overheating. No trapped moisture.</p>",
        "gg_slYWhic6_text": "<p><span style=\"color:#000000;font-size:20px;\"><strong>All-Day Comfort Fit</strong></span></p>",
        "ggh-2LrleT0_text": "<p>Designed to fit your body — not squeeze it.<br>Secure, flexible, and comfortable from morning to night, with no rolling or pressure points.</p>"
      }
    },
    "gp_section_603346966541238999": {
      "type": "gp-section-603346966541238999",
      "settings": {
        "checksum": "3c21fe2e21d4cacc674ccf4b03b22af5c6e6a534fdbc603e3c2c73c9c938d111_1_1_0_0__1",
        "ggFbP3xBmUz_text": "<p>4.8/5 based on 3438 reviews</p>",
        "ggFfmJmVkB0_text": "50,481+",
        "ggm2UZwe347_text": "<strong>Happy Customers</strong>",
        "ggOQn223jAY_text": "<span style=\"color:#000000;\"><strong>I Don’t Stress About My Body Anymore</strong></span>",
        "gg75QabjdPu_text": "<p>Some weeks I feel great, some weeks I don’t. This shirt keeps my waist looking clean no matter what. That consistency is everything for me.</p><p>&nbsp;</p><p><br>&nbsp;</p>",
        "ggHNFuI0l71_text": "<p>Rita j.</p>",
        "ggrx7TaRPAG_childItem_0": "<p>verified buyer</p>",
        "ggu0inijWlO_text": "<span style=\"color:#000000;\"><strong>Finally Something That Helps My Stomach Area</strong></span>",
        "ggcXAQ91KDn_text": "<p>I’ve lost weight everywhere except my stomach. This is the first thing that actually makes my belly look flatter without squeezing me. It doesn’t erase it, but it finally looks controlled.”</p><p>&nbsp;</p><p><br>&nbsp;</p>",
        "gglIUTOb2EW_text": "<p>Ariella d.</p>",
        "ggaluGpAhmk_childItem_0": "<p>verified buyer</p>",
        "gg-juWvQumi_text": "<strong>My Body Slimmed Down, My Belly Didn’t</strong>",
        "gg1G66oBGVt_text": "<p>My arms and legs got slimmer, but my stomach always looked bloated. This top smooths that area instantly and makes me feel way more put together.</p><p>&nbsp;</p><p><br>&nbsp;</p>",
        "ggcJyopJ7nO_text": "<p>Manon G.</p>",
        "ggKAqqMgj3l_childItem_0": "<p>verified buyer</p>",
        "ggvLcLK72wJ_text": "<strong>I Feel Put Together, Not Just Smaller</strong>",
        "ggUlXx8AFHZ_text": "<p>I didn’t want to disappear. I wanted to feel firm and confident. This shirt makes my body feel intentional, not unfinished.</p><p>&nbsp;</p>",
        "ggvof2xbeU3_text": "<p>Julia p.</p>",
        "ggdEQEorEOU_childItem_0": "<p>verified buyer</p>",
        "gg6EYqGLtfx_text": "<span style=\"color:#000000;\"><strong>I Didn’t Want to Be Thinner — I Wanted to Feel Better</strong></span>",
        "ggJWzAD8F2l_text": "<p>I lost weight but still felt soft and uncomfortable. This shirt makes everything feel supported, not loose. I finally like how I look again.</p><p>&nbsp;</p>",
        "ggQqkG8GPhi_text": "<p>Eva N.</p>",
        "ggsBjyjZNAA_childItem_0": "<p>verified buyer</p>",
        "ggS-0MZc9S5_text": "<span style=\"color:#000000;\"><strong>I saw the difference before the scale changed.</strong></span>",
        "ggDY6rR2w9l_text": "<p>I didn’t lose weight overnight, but my waist looked smoother and my posture was better within days. That alone made me feel more confident and motivated to stay consistent.</p>",
        "gg_-s9NAEN1_text": "<p>Lauren M.</p>",
        "ggo0YHXJCmq_childItem_0": "<p>verified buyer</p>",
        "ggkBWHyOGVm_text": "<span style=\"color:#000000;\"><strong>It feels supportive, not restrictive.</strong></span>",
        "ggOf_PAqLZX_text": "<p>I usually hate compression tops, but this one feels completely different. It’s comfortable, breathable, and I forget I’m wearing it. My back feels more supported, especially during long days.</p>",
        "ggL8OZ6aFm6_text": "<p>Laura f.</p>",
        "ggIedbP5z_W_childItem_0": "<p>verified buyer</p>",
        "ggFVxyqS3Td_text": "<span style=\"color:#000000;\">Impressive out of the box</span>",
        "ggvB1qHAbKh_text": "<p>Opened the box and was impressed right away. The brushed steel finish is clean and the dial has just the right amount of detail. Wears comfortably and looks great from every angle.</p>",
        "ggp2nu5CfOy_text": "<p>Katlin C.</p>",
        "ggSvqtfHZY__childItem_0": "<p>verified buyer</p>"
      }
    },
